propDescriptions.bottomAxis: Indicate which axis to display the the bottom of the charts. Can be a string (the id of the axis) or an object XAxisProps
propDescriptions.leftAxis: Indicate which axis to display the the left of the charts. Can be a string (the id of the axis) or an object YAxisProps
propDescriptions.rightAxis: Indicate which axis to display the the right of the charts. Can be a string (the id of the axis) or an object YAxisProps
propDescriptions.topAxis: Indicate which axis to display the the top of the charts. Can be a string (the id of the axis) or an object XAxisProps
